description:
&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for a dynamic person to take on this busy secretarial role within the surgical directorate. To join our busy team you will need, excellent communication skills, and a high degree of organisation skills, in order to provide the team with an effective and efficient Medical Secretarial Service to Consultants and Junior/Senior Medical Staff within the Directorate. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The position requires knowledge of a full range of secretarial procedures, a broad range of experience as a medical secretary, knowledge of the 18 week referral to treatment targets, be computer literate with experience of medical terminology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a part - time position, 30 hours over 5 working days. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Please read the Job Description before applying for this role. CV applications are not accepted.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameDaniel Bridgen-TaylorJob titleJunior Service ManagerTelephone number8687&lt;/p&gt;
